title: Check duties and customs procedures for exporting goods

heading_context: Check duties and customs procedures for exporting goods
chunks.html_content:
Find information about how to move goods from the UK to the rest of the world.

Use this service to check:

  • rules and restrictions
  • tax and duty rates
  • what exporting documents you need
chunks.plain_content:
Check duties and customs procedures for exporting goods
Find information about how to move goods from the UK to the rest of the world.

heading_context: Check duties and customs procedures for exporting goods
chunks.html_content: You need to be in the UK to use this service. If you’re a UK company overseas, contact the Department for Business and Trade (DBT).
chunks.plain_content:
Check duties and customs procedures for exporting goods
You need to be in the UK to use this service. If you’re a UK company overseas, contact the Department for Business and Trade (DBT).

heading_context: Check duties and customs procedures for exporting goods
chunks.html_content: You’ll need to know what your product is made of to get the correct information about how to export it.
chunks.plain_content:
Check duties and customs procedures for exporting goods
You’ll need to know what your product is made of to get the correct information about how to export it.

heading_context: Check duties and customs procedures for exporting goods
chunks.html_content: Example If you’re exporting chocolate, you’ll need to know if it contains added cereal, fruit or nuts.
